	       Given positive integers {\tt a} and {\tt d}, {\tt macaulayLowerOperator} yields {\tt a_<d>}, the operation from 
	       Green's proof of Macaulay's Theorem. See Bruns and Herzog, {\em Cohen-Macaulay Rings}, page 161.
